#=====================================================
# NOTES
#=====================================================
# Resolution Test Pattern:
#   - 7 point sources arranged along Z-axis
#   - Positions: 0, 1, 3, 6, 10, 15, 21 mm
#   - Spacing increases: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 mm
#   - Tests spatial resolution at mm-scale precision
#
# Ring Sources:
#   - 8 sizes: 0.1, 0.5, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 mm diameter
#   - 3 orientations per size: X, Y, Z aligned
#   - Total: 24 ring sources centered at (0, 30, 0) mm
#   - Tests resolution for different ring diameters
#
# Supported Tracers:
#   - Tc-99m: 140.5 keV (most common SPECT isotope)
#   - I-123:  159.0 keV (thyroid imaging)
#   - I-131:  364.0 keV (thyroid therapy)
#   - Tl-201:  71.0 keV (cardiac imaging)
#   - In-111: 171.0 keV (infection imaging)
#
# To change tracer: uncomment desired energy alias above
# To change activity: modify SOURCE_ACTIVITY alias
#
# Maximum source position (21 mm = 2.1 cm) fits within:
#   - 80 cm FOV (40 cm radius): YES
#   - 10 cm FOV (5 cm radius): YES
